flowchart TD
  A([Start]) --> B{Endpoint}
  B -->|POST /battles/start| C[Validate team and mode]
  C --> D[Generate seed and create battle session]
  D --> E[Return battle snapshot]

  B -->|POST /battles/:id/finish| F[Validate battle ownership and status]
  F --> G[Resolve result and summary]
  G --> H[Update session finished state]
  H --> I{Has rewards?}
  I -->|Yes| J[Grant rewards + write transactions]
  I -->|No| K[Skip reward grant]
  J --> L[Update leaderboard if needed]
  K --> L
  L --> M[Return final battle summary]

  E --> Z([End])
  M --> Z
